WEBVTT

00:06.705 --> 00:08.401
Previously on "Sanctuary"...

00:08.508 --> 00:09.805
The war has begun.

00:09.909 --> 00:11.433
Abnormals
in the path of the agent

00:11.611 --> 00:15.445
are showing rapid onset of clinical
paranoia and extreme aggression.

00:15.949 --> 00:17.917
Pitting humans
against abnormals,

00:18.084 --> 00:19.915
deciding who lives and who dies...

00:20.086 --> 00:21.553
The cabal has to be stopped.

00:21.721 --> 00:23.882
It's why I started this mission
more than a century ago.

00:24.324 --> 00:25.018
Dr. Watson?

00:25.191 --> 00:27.989
Not as in James Watson
who's a member of the Five?

00:28.161 --> 00:29.287
Why are you here, Druitt?

00:29.462 --> 00:31.953
Well, to save the world
as we know it, and, time allowing,

00:32.064 --> 00:35.034
reassert my superiority
in our battle of wits.

00:35.902 --> 00:37.062
Nigel Griffin is dead,

00:37.170 --> 00:39.638
but his powers were passed on
to his granddaughter, Clara.

00:42.475 --> 00:43.567
I just know
that we only have days

00:43.676 --> 00:46.236
to stop the destruction
of every abnormal on earth.

00:46.646 --> 00:49.012
It may well be that the source blood
could stop the disease

00:49.115 --> 00:51.583
in the form
of a synthesized antitoxin.

00:51.751 --> 00:52.775
Where did Gregory hide the vial?

00:52.952 --> 00:55.750
The lost city of Bhalasaam
in the Indian Himalayas.

00:55.922 --> 00:57.583
And he made sure
that only the five of us

00:57.757 --> 00:59.748
acting in concert could retrieve it.

01:00.226 --> 01:02.922
Which is a bit of a problem
if, in fact, I have killed Tesla.

01:03.029 --> 01:04.997
Hello, Nicola.

01:06.132 --> 01:07.030
It's all been destroyed.

01:07.133 --> 01:08.191
It's over.

01:08.368 --> 01:10.097
There has to be a way
into the labyrinth.

01:10.737 --> 01:13.934
Your mother and her colleagues
will no doubt try to stop us.

01:14.107 --> 01:16.007
I promise you they'll fail.

01:16.109 --> 01:20.546
They'll fail because you're going
to help us complete our plan.

01:25.585 --> 01:27.177
Where's Henry?

01:28.154 --> 01:29.985
Not far.

01:30.690 --> 01:34.091
- If you hurt him, I swear I will-
- Oh, we will hurt him.

01:34.260 --> 01:35.989
In fact, the quality and quantity

01:36.162 --> 01:38.687
of what remains of his life
very much depends on you.

01:40.166 --> 01:42.066
I'll tell you whatever you want.
Just let Henry live.

01:42.235 --> 01:45.363
Is that what you think we are?
Killers, murderers?

01:45.538 --> 01:48.996
That bioweapon you set off?
Not exactly charity work.

01:49.109 --> 01:51.839
In fact, that's exactly what it is.

01:52.011 --> 01:55.242
A helping hand to the humans so
that they can clearly see the threat

01:55.348 --> 01:57.646
to the very survival
of our species.

01:57.817 --> 01:59.512
You're starting a war.

01:59.619 --> 02:00.643
We're controlling our destiny.

02:00.753 --> 02:03.449
Most of the abnormals out there
are peaceful. They aren't a threat.

02:03.556 --> 02:06.491
Every abnormal we don't control
is a threat, Ashley.

02:06.659 --> 02:09.321
Despite your mother's
propaganda.

02:09.596 --> 02:12.656
How many so-called peaceful
abnormals have you destroyed?

02:15.735 --> 02:17.293
You know...

02:18.571 --> 02:19.868
I like your mother.

02:20.640 --> 02:22.665
There was a time
I even admired her,

02:22.842 --> 02:24.867
but we are fighting
for humanity's survival,

02:24.978 --> 02:27.378
and she's chosen the wrong side.

02:28.047 --> 02:31.210
Are you ready to choose yours?

02:33.000 --> 02:39.074
